{"tid":2099894,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蓬佩奧讚揚科企拒絕向香港政府交出用戶數據，鼓勵其他公司也應這樣做","createTime":"2020-07-08T15:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T15:20:39.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81a06a9f057a32e4543ee4a5770528e75a1a7916","tid":2099894,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:10:22.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧感謝Google，Facebook和Twitter，讚揚他們拒絕向香港特區政府交出用戶數據，他鼓勵其他公司也這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧說，北京承諾賦予香港高度自治五十年不變，但僅僅二十三年後所發生的一切，證實是空洞的諾言。<br />\n<br />\n「港區國安法」43條列明，警方有權要求移除電子平台，可能構成危害國家安全的信息，或者要求服務商提供身分紀錄或解密。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536650-20200708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536650-20200708.htm&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=e89f600f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536650-20200708.htm&h=abefd3bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536650-20200708.htm</a>"},{"pid":"45333308d1d888db9e5d21f442ed078bdadbd69f","tid":2099894,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:16:10.000Z","msg":"侵 人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15aaa4dafb055e054337f8b393a8f95c30acf3e0","tid":2099894,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45333308d1d888db9e5d21f442ed078bdadbd69f","tid":2099894,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:16:10.000Z","msg":"侵 人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"追緊黃豆數  唔得閒"},{"pid":"19b1be57ed2f7dfe1921b6643a95a62bb5629d4d","tid":2099894,"uid":98289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45333308d1d888db9e5d21f442ed078bdadbd69f","tid":2099894,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTi